**Privacy Policy**
Last Updated: April 19, 2026

This Privacy Policy describes how Pollito Productions handles information when you play Zen Pop Lounge.

**1. Information We Collect**
Because this App is a web-based game, certain information is processed automatically:

* **Technical Data:** We may collect basic technical information such as your device type, operating system version, and IP address to ensure the game displays correctly.
* **Usage Data:** We may collect information on how the App is used, such as session duration and high scores, to improve the gameplay experience.

**2. How We Use Information**
We use the collected information solely to:

* Provide and maintain the App’s functionality.
* Monitor and analyze usage to improve the user experience.
* Ensure the security and integrity of the App.

**3. Data Sharing & Advertising**
We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties. However, *Zen Pop Lounge* uses Google AdMob to provide a rewarded video ad. AdMob is a third-party service that may collect and use basic device data (like your device's advertising ID) to serve these ads. To learn exactly what data Google collects and how it is used, please read the [Google Privacy Policy](https://policies.google.com/privacy).

**4. Children’s Privacy**
Our App is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal identifiable information from children. If you are a parent and believe your child has provided us with information, please contact us.

**5. Third-Party Links**
The App may contain links to the original web version of the game. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites.

**6. Changes to This Policy**
We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

**7. Contact Us**
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: pollitoproductions.dev@gmail.com
